# game/Scenes/Lisa/LisaConversations/lisas8.rpy:13
translate chinese lisas8_e7a7180d:

    # sp "Oh geez, I have no idea."
    sp "哦天哪，我完全不知道。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/LisaConversations/lisas8.rpy:14
translate chinese lisas8_45f17f75:

    # sp "I feel like I've been struggling with that my whole life."
    sp "感觉我这一辈子都在为此苦恼。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/LisaConversations/lisas8.rpy:16
translate chinese lisas8_9ee67d09:

    # sp "I've never found anything I felt like I was really good at. Just things I can do to keep my head above the water."
    sp "我从来没找到过什么觉得自己特别擅长的事。只有些勉强能让我维持生计的活儿。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/LisaConversations/lisas8.rpy:17
translate chinese lisas8_338d6102:

    # sp "Barely."
    sp "勉强而已。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/LisaConversations/lisas8.rpy:18
translate chinese lisas8_924b0ff6:

    # pc "I'm sure there's plenty you're good at, [mom]."
    pc "我相信你肯定有很多擅长的事，[mom]。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/LisaConversations/lisas8.rpy:20
translate chinese lisas8_426e5f78:

    # pc "I know you're good at cooking, at cleaning, and decorating the house. Stuff like that."
    pc "我知道你擅长做饭、打扫卫生和布置房子。这类事情。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/LisaConversations/lisas8.rpy:22
translate chinese lisas8_52782eb1:

    # sp "At being a stay-at-home mom? Yeah I guess I'm pretty good at that."
    sp "当全职妈妈？是啊，我想我在这方面还挺在行的。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/LisaConversations/lisas8.rpy:24
translate chinese lisas8_47418b74:

    # sp "The pay is shit though."
    sp "不过报酬少得可怜。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/LisaConversations/lisas8.rpy:25
translate chinese lisas8_7ec499d2:

    # pc "Ha, I guess so. I'm sure there's something there you could turn into a job though."
    pc "哈，确实是。但我相信其中肯定有些能变成工作的。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/LisaConversations/lisas8.rpy:27
translate chinese lisas8_1b796563:

    # sp "Like what? A cook? Interior decorator? House cleaner? Nanny?"
    sp "比如什么？厨师？室内设计师？保洁员？保姆？"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/LisaConversations/lisas8.rpy:28
translate chinese lisas8_cd9f00ec:

    # sp "I mean, I'd do any of those if I had to, but I don't think that they would pay as much as what I'm making right now."
    sp "我的意思是，如果非做不可，这些我都能做，但我觉得它们的报酬肯定不如我现在赚的多。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/LisaConversations/lisas8.rpy:29
translate chinese lisas8_f07093b6:

    # pc "But maybe you would be happier?"
    pc "但也许你会更快乐？"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/LisaConversations/lisas8.rpy:30
translate chinese lisas8_f267d91a:

    # pc "How much you make isn't as important as your happiness."
    pc "赚多少钱并不比你的幸福重要。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/LisaConversations/lisas8.rpy:32
translate chinese lisas8_7542dd83:

    # sp "It is when you have a mortgage."
    sp "当你背负房贷时，它就很重要了。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/LisaConversations/lisas8.rpy:34
translate chinese lisas8_7ecfe161:

    # sp "You're right though. If there was another job that I thought I'd be happier at and still be able to pay the bills, I'd take it."
    sp "不过你说得对。如果真有份工作，我觉得在那儿会更开心，还能付得起账单，那我肯定会去。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/LisaConversations/lisas8.rpy:35
translate chinese lisas8_7cdb4501:

    # sp "But really, my job isn't awful or anything. Maybe I just complain about it too much."
    sp "但说真的，我的工作也没那么糟糕。也许我只是抱怨得太多了。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/LisaConversations/lisas8.rpy:36
translate chinese lisas8_058f9372:

    # sp "It's nothing special, just collecting debts, but somebody has to do it, right?"
    sp "这工作没什么特别的，就是收账，但总得有人做，对吧？"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/LisaConversations/lisas8.rpy:37
translate chinese lisas8_183359e4:

    # pc "Yeah, I guess so. I just want you to be happy, [mom]."
    pc "是啊，大概吧。我只是希望你开心，[mom]。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/LisaConversations/lisas8.rpy:39
translate chinese lisas8_8b801291:

    # sp "I know, baby. I am happy."
    sp "我知道，亲爱的。我很开心。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/LisaConversations/lisas8.rpy:40
translate chinese lisas8_d741e7be:

    # sp "Work is work, you know..."
    sp "工作就是工作嘛……"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/LisaConversations/lisas8.rpy:41
translate chinese lisas8_eae28474:

    # sp "But coming home to you and Suzy makes me very happy."
    sp "但回家见到你和苏茜，真的让我很开心。"

